name: Sticky Note Kit
description:
Figma is the future. Did you know Figma is perfect for remote ideation? I found myself duplicating this file with sticky notes over and over. Now it’s time for you to duplicate it! 

Inside the most basic Figma file ever you’ll find: 
• 2 sizes of stickies 
• 4 colours of stickies
• Extra-strength adhesion (they never fall off the wall!)
• No unreadable handwriting!

 Cheers. ✌️
